Duduzane Zuma, a son of  South
Africa ’s President  Jacob Zuma , said critics of his ties to
the Gupta family and their business dealings should take
him to court or “leave us the hell alone.”  Kagiso Securities will release its February Purchasing
Managers Index for South Africa at 11 a.m. after it rose to
54.6 in January, indicating the manufacturing industry us
expanding.  Marthinus van Schalkwyk, the country’s tourism
minister, will announce tourist arrival figures for 2010,
the year in which South Africa hosted the soccer  World Cup .  To contact the reporter on this story:
